  <bannerDropdown><![CDATA[Ski Holidays]]></bannerDropdown>
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>If you own a website or are a keen blogger and would like to be rewarded for promoting our holidays on your site, join our successful <strong>affiliate programme</strong> and earn commission on all online bookings driven by your website.</p>
<h2><strong>Who are we</strong></h2>
<p>As an award-winning specialist independent tour operator with over 80 years experience, <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/b49585f93afa4fa9bb0bf506c7aa71da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b49585f93afa4fa9bb0bf506c7aa71da}" title="Home">Inghams</a></strong> is one of the strongest and well established brands in the travel industry and offers top quality winter and summer holidays. Our winter holiday range includes <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e}" title="Ski Holidays">skiing and snowboarding holidays</a></strong>, short <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">winter breaks to Lapland</a></strong> and <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/63d3751ab6044b7c82e72f82f4d64e39" href="/{localLink:umb://document/63d3751ab6044b7c82e72f82f4d64e39}" title="Lapland/Finland">Santa breaks</a></strong>. Our summer Lakes &amp; Mountains programme offers an even wider choice of scenic getaways – from <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">holidays to Europe’s finest Lakes &amp; Mountains resorts</a></strong> to <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/539bfdab944543f78d709f911b410db9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/539bfdab944543f78d709f911b410db9}" title="City Breaks">city breaks</a></strong> and <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/731184fa7b9742f0a969771e90773289" href="/{localLink:umb://document/731184fa7b9742f0a969771e90773289}" title="Tours and Multi-Centre Holidays">tours</a></strong>. Our holidays are perfect for couples, <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/7dbdfaaa8cb844fab907811da9fe4079" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7dbdfaaa8cb844fab907811da9fe4079}" title="Family Holidays">families</a></strong> as well as <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0be000e76fd24338ab52cce21f5c819d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0be000e76fd24338ab52cce21f5c819d}" title="Singles Holidays">solo travellers</a></strong>.</p>
<h2><strong>How does it work</strong></h2>
<p>Simply promote our holidays on your website by including a banner or a link to our site – whenever someone books a holiday after clicking on one of those links you will receive a percentage of the booking value. To ensure smooth integration and full transparency, our affiliate programme runs on the <strong><a rel="nofollow noopener" href="http://www.affiliatewindow.com/uk/" target="_blank">Affiliate Window network</a></strong>. Join it for free to gain access to our links and creative banners and to monitor your earnings in real time. Your commission will be paid out promptly as soon as the holiday has been completed.<br /><br /></p>
<h2><strong>Why work with us</strong></h2>
<p><em>-    Excellent volume of online bookings</em><br /><em>-    High booking value</em><br /><em>-    Low cancellation rate</em><br /><em>-    Average 2.5% commission on all online bookings</em><br /><em>-    Potential to earn higher commission rates in return for extra exposure</em><br /><em>-    Responsive website</em><br /><em>-    27.5% average growth in revenue for our Top 20 affiliates YOY</em><br /><em>-    45 day cookie</em><br /><em>-    99.6% affiliate bookings approved</em><br /><em><strong><br /></strong></em></p>
<h2><strong>Join the programme</strong></h2>
<p>If you would like to work with us, <strong><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://darwin.affiliatewindow.com/merchant-profile/3206" target="_blank">simply click here to join our programme via Affiliate Window</a></strong>. If you have any queries, please do not hesitate to contact our <strong>Affiliate Team</strong> at: <strong><a href="mailto:affiliates@inghams.co.uk">affiliates@inghams.co.uk</a></strong> or alternatively call <strong>01483 791 052</strong>.</p>
<p>We look forward to working with you!</p>]]></bodyText>
